reviewText: Gripping....storyline is real. Hollywood caliber acting, I loved it and am gladly adding it to my collection of films. I will be following these guys work from now on.
THE ACTING WAS BAD.MUST HAVE HAD A SMALL BUDGET. BUT I DIDN'T PAY MUCH TO BUY IT EITHER AND GLAD FOR THAT

Let me be the first person NOT involved with this... uh... "film", to give my two cents.  It's more or less a really bad high school play videotaped by a blind person.  Honestly, if the whole thing wasn't so depressing, it would be funny. And the most depressing part of all?  I paid $1.99 to see it.

This movie is a roller coaster ride from beginning to end. Very intense and suspenseful. The acting is superb and can only be described as AWESOME! If you like suspense thrillers, this is one to watch.

I watched this movie and it was awesome. The actors are great and the twist to the movie will keep you in suspense. You would never believe that a suspense thriller can do that, but pick up a copy and experience it for yourself.
This movie is trutly awesome from begining until the end, you will be holding on to your seat, a must see film Rated R.
